      "type": "p",
      "text": "groupby()把迭代器中相邻的重复元素挑出来放在一起："
    },
    {
      "type": "pre",
      "text": ">>> for key, group in itertools.groupby('AAABBBCCAAA'):\n...     print(key, list(group))\n...\nA ['A', 'A', 'A']\nB ['B', 'B', 'B']\nC ['C', 'C']\nA ['A', 'A', 'A']"
    },
